As a user(customer) 
I want to be able to order scooter rent
So that I can use services proposed by online shop

Scope

The scooter rent functionality
The posibility order scooter rent using phone number
It should work in Chorome, Mozilla, Safari brousers
It should also works in Mobile


Pre condition:

The Customer is registered in online shop
The "Our services" page functionality is implemented


Acceptance criteria:


Scenario 1:User can sucesfully rent a scooter by fill clasic form
Given: User is in the "Our services" page
When: Click on the "Scooters for rent " button 
And: Fill all required fields
And:Select the type of vehicle
And:Click on the "Send" button
Then: The request is sent. The rent is booked


Scenario 1:User can sucesfully rent a scooter by quick form
Given: User is in the "Our services" page
When: Click on the "Scooters for rent " button 
And: Fill phone number field
And:Click on the "Send" button
Then:Get call from online shop, discus all details and book the rent














